WEBVTT

00:08:58.989 --> 00:09:00.893
We see that it works.

00:09:02.006 --> 00:09:05.172
We think this can be done everywhere,

00:09:05.196 --> 00:09:07.396
because this is not for the rich.

00:09:07.863 --> 00:09:12.212
We've been doing this with the same budget

00:09:12.236 --> 00:09:16.315
as any traditional nursing home
has in our country.

00:09:16.339 --> 00:09:19.116
We work only with the state budget.

00:09:20.220 --> 00:09:27.092
(Applause)

00:09:28.226 --> 00:09:31.798
Because it has to do
with thinking different,